  <Strings>
    <Section>Main Text</Section>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>やったぞ！
俺は、甘口カレーを守り抜いたんだ！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>I did it! I protected the sweet curry!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>28</SpeakerId>
      <Id>1</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>よかったわね、アスベル</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>I'm happy for you, Asbel.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>29</SpeakerId>
      <Id>2</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>ん？
シェリア、なにを作っているんだ？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Huh? Cheria, what's that you're making?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>28</SpeakerId>
      <Id>3</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>今日の夕飯の焼き鳥丼よ。
アスベルの分もたっぷり作ってあるから
これから一週間はずっと焼き鳥丼ね♪</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>It's my grilled chicken rice bowl for dinner. I made
plenty for you too, so we'll be having grilled
chicken rice bowls every day for the next week. ♪</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>29</SpeakerId>
      <Id>4</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>…………</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>.........</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>28</SpeakerId>
      <Id>5</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>守れなかった……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>I couldn't protect us...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>28</SpeakerId>
      <Id>6</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
